{"tid":1566012,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你個嘴，好多英文版香港國歌唔撚啱beat既","createTime":"2019-09-13T11:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T17:38:55.000Z","uid":269619,"like":39,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"39d5e58df5d450ecf7ace2d35fba66ee07fae868","tid":1566012,"uid":269619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:23:23.000Z","msg":"要外國注意，但d詞又填得唔好，點得到外國注意呀？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我個英國佬frd睇唔過眼幫手譯多次<br />\n（P牌推唔到，入黎唔該同我推爆佢，等有合唱團唱呢個版。）<br />\n<br />\nLyricist: Dr. N<br />\n<br />\nWith tears of the land in our skies,<br />\nWith pain in our hearts, in our cries!<br />\nStand fast, everyone, and as one we rise --<br />\nCan you hear our people's song?<br />\n<br />\nFor we who must face all our fears,<br />\nFor we who will fight for what is dear:<br />\nTo arms citizens, for the hounds draw near --<br />\nGive your heart to save Hong Kong!<br />\n<br />\nFrom the night, a darkness fills the air!<br />\nFrom the mist a fiery people's light shall sing --<br />\n&quot;Join with me, the people you'll save,<br />\nFight on and be brave,<br />\nA Revolution of our Time!&quot;<br />\n<br />\nAnd in the dawn we shall fight for Hong Kong,<br />\nMy friends we march for our freedom everlong!<br />\nAll advance, hand-in-hand, as we cheer in song,<br />\nSing it now: &quot;Glory, Hong Kong!&quot;"},{"pid":"f1c0ae6a590e071d305d1f38e183b9d2cbf3904e","tid":1566012,"uid":19252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:26:13.000Z","msg":"你個英國frd 識中文？"},{"pid":"d277d1eb2a790ba8e652ac52d4811d49f72a14bd","tid":1566012,"uid":321732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:26:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69eac30753e7ea89e23f403b89e38f3b9565027b","tid":1566012,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi